Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:17.91,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:19.46,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:34.41,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:38.24,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Since I become a spirit, all I can do is watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:40.05,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.01,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,This is bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:44.30,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,This is bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:46.07,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You humans sure are selfish, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:50.54,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't care when seven \Nbillion people died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:53.11,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yet one person dies, \Nand you're crying and screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:55.20,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean a damn thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:57.18,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:59.37,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:02.39,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the cold one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:04.09,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.16,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:07.54,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:13.09,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You just said you couldn't do anything, \Nbut maybe you just {\i1}didn't{\i0} do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:15.59,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:18.14,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in telling me that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:19.51,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.85,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... I just have to go back in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:27.97,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,True, with your current spirit power level,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you could land anywhere you want \Nto in the space-time valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:34.41,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:35.72,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Something I need?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:38.83,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,A strong desire to save someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:44.12,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Without that, you'll bounce off \Nthe curved surface of space-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:45.21,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I do—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:46.57,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Once you bounce off, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:49.49,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be able to come \Nback to this world again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:51.00,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.79,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:55.63,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Make a strong wish, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:57.87,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Towards your own soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:01.53,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Ito, I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:03.31,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:05.62,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:07.38,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Ito...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:09.07,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Ito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:18.99,Punchline-Ep_Title2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,#05
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:18.99,Punchline-Ep_Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Ito Dies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:37.20,Punchline-Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Punch Line
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:00.76,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Am I back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:12.75,Punchline-Ito_Emails,Text,0000,0000,0000,,From: {\c&HF1E262&\b1}frontier-headman@xxx.xx.jp{\c\b0}\N To: {\c&HF1E262&\b1}Hikiotani Ito{\c\b0}\NDecember 29 7:24 P.M. \N\NThere's been a second victim. \NRaishi Moena.\NIf you don't want to lose any \Nmore classmates, come to\N Ishinogari Shrine at ten tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:11.00,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:15.56,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault that Meiko and Moena...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:17.98,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,You know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:21.99,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, now you know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:26.61,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Ito went to the shrine according \Nto the email's demands, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:29.16,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,The person who sent the email killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:31.16,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:34.92,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the reason, you can't \Nlet Ito go to the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:38.29,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you need to worry about right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.80,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty minutes left until it's time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:46.02,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Mikatan, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:47.89,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.75,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Rabura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.94,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:56.95,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:59.68,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,The air's getting stale here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bleah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:12.83,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.29,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you two make up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:21.68,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:26.66,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, um... Have you seen the \Nprotective charm that was in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:27.95,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:29.08,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.76,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be... a poltergeist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:32.89,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:34.98,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:42.26,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:46.03,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Narugino, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:48.05,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Ito's life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:52.30,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,That Burabura chick seriously pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:53.90,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Meika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.32,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Ito?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:00.88,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Can you keep him for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.58,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:06.28,Punchline-Names,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Raishi Moena (17) \NChouka Rina (17) \NNamado Suisei (17) \NShujo Manoto (17) \NKoto Monami (17)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:07.75,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying all the people whose \Nnames are in this video were killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:08.42,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:10.17,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:11.76,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry to Ito-chan's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.02,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,My boobs... My boobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:19.02,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:21.16,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:23.74,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:24.93,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.57,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.73,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I know about the emails, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:30.79,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.83,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.08,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Ito-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:42.21,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go, no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:44.51,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,because it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:47.63,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault those two people were...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.14,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Ito-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.10,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.13,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:53.96,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:55.72,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I never will!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.89,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to the shrine, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:00.21,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.77,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.31,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:06.90,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Because, Ito-chan, you're... You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my precious friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:17.77,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Mikatan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:25.07,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Umbeijini nyopurasara...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:30.20,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put a spell on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:30.20,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What's that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:32.57,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magic song to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.29,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Ishigata-san taught it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:36.31,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Ishigata-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.01,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.43,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,See...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:42.17,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,He was a researcher at this \Nplace called Yuba Labs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:46.73,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I was—I mean, {\i1}we{\i0} were born \Nand raised at that lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.57,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Yuba Labs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:52.11,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,They used to do research \Non genetics and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:56.58,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,There were two other kids at the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.32,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,A boy and a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.16,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,We were together from birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.33,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,They both helped me out so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.58,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyo,0000,0000,0000,,No, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:07.58,Punchline-Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:08.84,Punchline-Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Settle down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:09.59,Punchline-Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:12.36,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyo,0000,0000,0000,,No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:14.23,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.96,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Pine! Guri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.89,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of Chiyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:22.47,Punchline-Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:30.07,Punchline-Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,You kids have the ability to Yubafy, \Nyet you never use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.65,Punchline-Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:35.53,Punchline-Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,The only way I can find out is to take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:38.87,Punchline-Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,I have to cut open your heads \Nand look inside your brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.45,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:41.58,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Pine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:43.91,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Pine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:44.84,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:50.17,Punchline-Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I damaged my precious test subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:52.13,Punchline-Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:55.67,Punchline-Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be cutting you up eventually anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:59.68,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have Chiyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:00.97,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.23,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,Never...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:04.14,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.68,Punchline-Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:11.94,Punchline-Flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,That's the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.56,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Did you like that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.66,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Wh-Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:22.89,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.62,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:27.90,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Ito-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:28.65,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.47,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any crushes, or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.74,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really a crush,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there is someone I like as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.14,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:41.94,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,A teacher at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.84,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,He's my homeroom teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.79,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,but he's like a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:53.84,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,One time, he gave me a ride home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:57.61,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,He was worried it'd be dangerous, \Nsince it was getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.37,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Some kids in my class saw us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:05.87,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,The next day, when I went to school, \Nno one would talk to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:07.94,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:11.83,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,There was a girl who liked that teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:16.22,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,She was like the leader of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.50,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,She targeted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:22.13,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,That's when it started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.19,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Every day was hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:34.11,Punchline-Die,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Die
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:34.11,Punchline-Math,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Math
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:28.40,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how many times \NI bought new pairs of indoor shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:32.53,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,My textbooks and notebooks \Nwere rendered unreadable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to keep throwing them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:38.92,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,On days when we had P.E., I stayed \Nin my track suit until after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:40.85,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,because my skirt would get stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.79,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,My underwear went missing one \Ntime when we had swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:49.83,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,That much I could bear, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:54.71,Punchline-Flashback,Moena,0000,0000,0000,,Ew, there's gum in your hair, Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:56.59,Punchline-Flashback,Rumi,0000,0000,0000,,You put it there, didn't you, Moena?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.36,Punchline-Flashback,Moena,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:01.22,Punchline-Flashback,Rumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. Let's cut it out for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.22,Punchline-Flashback,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.13,Punchline-Flashback,Moena,0000,0000,0000,,Good going, Meiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:06.34,Punchline-Flashback,Rumi,0000,0000,0000,,Nice cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:08.10,Punchline-Flashback,Meiko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I cut too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:14.23,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I stopped going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:19.38,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, my teacher was nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:23.38,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever talked to him about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:24.71,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:27.47,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to give him trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.72,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason for the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:32.37,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,The video?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.53,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You said you saw it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:37.34,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:43.21,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,The names on it are the names \Nof the kids who bullied me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:47.32,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to scare them \Na little, so I put it online.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:50.31,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,But your name was in the video, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.63,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't on there when I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:54.69,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:57.57,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Someone edited it afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.66,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whoever it was that killed Meiko and Moena.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:04.82,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say somethi—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.32,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,How could I have admitted
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.93,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,that I was being bullied at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:09.91,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:12.65,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious? Because I'd look stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:14.15,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I'd look pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:20.02,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a loner. I'm not shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.73,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I could make new friends easily if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:26.39,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wanted them to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:28.34,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to show them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:32.26,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I knew no one really thought that of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:39.63,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, ever since I saw that video,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:42.32,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I've been really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:47.12,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,But whenever I saw everyone smiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:52.11,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,it started to feel like none of it was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.60,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Ito-chan, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.50,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:01.00,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the side of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.62,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.82,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.26,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:11.07,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:17.22,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like history's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:18.77,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:20.97,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:23.52,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,There's too much to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.57,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.22,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.74,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:13:56.90,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you two are getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.19,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.03,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,He just keeps clinging to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:04.94,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Shoo, shoo! Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:08.28,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You've been with him since \Nlast night, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:10.69,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you take care of him for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:16.66,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, y'know, he saved me one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:18.52,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:22.06,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:25.67,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,There was some noise in the satellite link,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.26,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,so I came to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.23,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:32.05,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um... It doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:35.30,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I came to take Muhi, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.35,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Take him, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.61,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,One more day until New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:58.87,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Mikatan, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:01.35,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.47,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:13.58,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Meika?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:15.15,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.48,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Meika!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:24.78,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:25.98,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Muhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:27.28,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Muhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.95,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.29,0:15:31.45,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,What man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.70,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.58,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,The one who was here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.50,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.12,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Muhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.20,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.20,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,There's still more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.41,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,More?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.08,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:47.71,Punchline-Flashback,Kame,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Ito that this is punishment \Nfor not having come last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.97,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,It was Turtle Man that \Ncalled Ito out last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:52.68,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Ito-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:57.22,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle Man is the one who \Nkilled Ito's classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:16:00.10,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,If Ito runs into him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.19,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Ito!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.11,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:07.11,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.11,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:11.06,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Turtle Man here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:13.65,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,He might have run far off by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.09,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so nonchalant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:17.10,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What if right now—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:19.66,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try luring him out, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.41,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Email!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.92,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.92,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to send a reply \Nto Ito's email from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:36.64,Punchline-Yuta_Email,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Sender: {\b1}Hikiotani Ito{\b0} \N\NSubject:{\b1} No Title{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:32.57,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,"Please come to the Korai House rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:34.85,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here right now."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:36.64,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, send!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:42.73,Punchline-Level_Up,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:43.99,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.35,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.98,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,The jar of cinnamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:48.54,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:50.03,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,There was another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:52.89,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Were you thinking of using Rabura's body
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to fight against Turtle Man or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.04,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I have another plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.58,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:06.67,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,All right, almost done with repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:10.61,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What could I use to beat Turtle Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:13.51,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! A stun gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.31,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:17.56,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen these before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:18.35,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:21.66,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're a genius, Meika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:25.32,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I still have more amazing stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:26.60,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:28.54,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Face Maker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:31.06,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,It's basically a disguise mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:34.03,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.47,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:39.16,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,You can look like anyone, \Nif you have 3D data of their head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:41.87,Punchline-Flashback,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's totally Rabura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:43.92,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's change my voice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:48.68,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Using this tiny voice changer, Voice Maker...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:53.96,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, I'm Ito-chan, and I love BL.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.97,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Chiranosuke, I have a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:12.08,Punchline-Yuta_Email2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF9E334&}Cancel{\c} {\b1\c&H494B4B&}New Message{\b0} {\c&HF9E334&\b1}Send{\c\b0} \N\NTo: {\c&HF9E334&\b1}Daihatsu Meika, Chichibu Rabura{\c\b0}\N\N Sender: {\b1}Hikiotani Ito{\b0} \N\NSubject:{\b1} No Title{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:03.75,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,"To: Meika, Rabura."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:07.98,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,"Turtle Man is headed to \Nthe Korai House rooftop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Do what you can \Ntogether to defeat him!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:15.93,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,When you say you have a plan, you really mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:18.53,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:22.03,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, those two can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:25.46,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Muhi, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:26.54,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Muhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.42,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Ito-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:33.84,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes, just like the email said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.88,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:42.66,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call a cease fire for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:43.75,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Cease fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:46.10,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,We were in the middle of a fight, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.10,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:50.89,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.08,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:55.32,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's begin the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.41,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Now, bring it on, Turtle Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:12.32,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, she changes her appearance \Nto draw the enemy's attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura holds his arms from behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they finish him with the stun gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.26,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Was that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.42,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.94,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like it'll work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:28.36,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.52,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:34.94,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.08,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,You're not Ito, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:38.06,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:41.70,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ito-chan, and I love BL.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.57,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Moe moe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:46.12,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Totally moe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:47.29,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.57,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.25,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.90,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.76,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:04.09,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me, if you're going to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:05.43,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:06.41,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:07.68,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Just run—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.86,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this is a toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.66,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,I... I was just
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about to cut you off like a badass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:27.20,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd shoot first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:29.45,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This can't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.16,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:36.56,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I said some awful things to Meika.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.17,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have her dying on me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.68,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, you can go first—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.51,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,No you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:59.45,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.15,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Losing neither to rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:05.49,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,nor to the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:09.61,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,nor to snow, nor to the heat of summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:12.36,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,with a strong body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:25.03,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Without desire, never losing temper, \Nand always smiling quietly.
